| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5257 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 941e477e-376c-5976-8c61-5def736b584c"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
